OL,3,CIran bets it can push for peace on its
OL,4,Cterms or return to war
OL,6,FAs Donald Trump publicly claimed he
OL,7,Fwas going to stop an Israeli response,
OL,8,Fthe counterattack began. The targets,
OL,9,Fmilitary sites and energy sites in
OL,10,FTehran and across the country.
OL,12,FThe cycle will likely continue into
OL,13,Fthe days ahead. None of it bodes well
OL,14,Ffor President Trump's claim of an
OL,15,Fimminent deal nor for the global
OL,16,Feconomy. Oil prices have already risen.
