OL,3,CIran bets it can push for peace on its
OL,4,Cterms or return to war
OL,6,FTricky also for those relations with
OL,7,FGulf allies. President Trump's vocal
OL,8,Fclaims that he was going to stop any
OL,9,Fresponse are likely to have been a
OL,10,Fperformative attempt to be seen to be
OL,11,Fdoing something by those whose
OL,12,Fcountries may see the force of Iranian
OL,13,Freaction.
OL,15,FThe conversations between the
OL,16,Fleadership in Israel and Washington
OL,17,Fhave often been less forceful in
OL,18,Fprivate than in public and this
OL,19,Fadministration is no different.
OL,21,FSirens could be heard in Amman, Jordan
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
