OL,3,CIran bets it can push for peace on its
OL,4,Cterms or return to war
OL,6,FWhat this also speaks to is a
OL,7,Fcontinuing miscalculation of Iran's
OL,8,Fmilitary position. When, 100 days ago,
OL,9,Fthis war began, the view from Israel
OL,10,Fand the USA was that it would be over
OL,11,Fswiftly, with a crushing defeat of the
OL,12,FIslamic Republic. That has not come to
OL,13,Fpass.
OL,15,FAfter 40 days of war, Iran is still
OL,16,Ffiring and remains a military force.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
