OL,3,CIran bets it can push for peace on its
OL,4,Cterms or return to war
OL,6,FSixty days on, taking the fight back
OL,7,Fto the Israelis, and in effect the
OL,8,FAmericans, shows that Iran is far from
OL,9,Fa spent force. That it decided to act
OL,10,Ffor an ally, Hezbollah, in another
OL,11,Fcountry, Lebanon, has the air of
OL,12,Fleadership feeling confident instead
OL,13,Fof cowed by war.
OL,15,FAnd why would they not? They have held
OL,16,Fout this long and now have a chokehold
OL,17,Fover global shipping and, therefore,
OL,18,Fthe global economy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
