OL,3,CIran bets it can push for peace on its
OL,4,Cterms or return to war
OL,6,FSo long as they have the Strait, they
OL,7,Fhave the power, and for now there is
OL,8,Fno sign of any agreement to open it.
OL,10,FIran has gambled it can afford to push
OL,11,Ffor peace on its terms and also afford
OL,12,Fto return to war.
